n punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>To hide the tooltips:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code>controller<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tooptip<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>","excerpt":"To show the tooltips: To hide the tooltips:","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"Adding Tooltips"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"docs/adding-tooltips.md"}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/docs/adding-tooltips/"}}